ebt-forgiveness-biden-campaign-promises-education-department-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epledge%3C%2Fa%3E%20Biden%20made%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20to%20cancel%20student%20debt%20for%20borrowers%20from%20public%20colleges%20and%20universities%20earning%20up%20to%20%24125%2C000%20per%20year%2C%20and%20from%20private%20HBCUs%20and%20minority-serving%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debt%20that%20was%20eliminated%20is%20not%20federal%20student%20debt%2C%20but%20rather%2C%20institutional%20debt%20that%20a%20college%20owns%2C%20like%20unpaid%20tuition%20and%20other%20school-related%20expenses.%20Schools%20have%20the%20power%20to%20withhold%20transcripts%20and%20diplomas%20until%20that%20debt%20is%20paid%20off%2C%20which%20could%20limit%20students'%20post-graduation%20employment%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20of%202022%2C%20the%20Debt%20Collective%20took%20the%20same%20action%20for%20former%20Bennett%20College%20students%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loans-wiped-out-bennett-college-debt-collective-hbcu-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeliminating%20%241.7%20million%20in%20college%20debt%20for%20462%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20dating%20back%20as%20far%20as%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20Debt%20Collective%20is%20calling%20for%20Biden%20to%20act%20on%20federal%20student%20debt%20for%20all%20borrowers.%20Last%20year%2C%20Biden%20announced%20up%20to%20%2420%2C000%20in%20student%20debt%20for%20federal%20borrowers%20making%20under%20%24125%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20but%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruck%20down%20the%20relief%20in%20June%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20the%20president%20did%20not%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20cancel%20debt%20broadly%20using%20the%20HEROES%20Act%20of%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20s