a%20senior%20analyst%20at%20StorageCafe%2C%20said%20that%20Gen%20Z%20doesn't%20have%20the%20same%20location%20preferences%20as%20older%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGen%20Zers%20are%20increasingly%20drawn%20to%20simpler%20living%20in%20their%20housing%20choices%2C%26quot%3B%20Mann%20told%20Insider%20via%20email.%20%26quot%3BUnlike%20millennials%2C%20who%20often%20gravitate%20to%20DC%2C%20Washington%2C%20and%20Illinois%2C%20Gen%20Zers%20tend%20to%20favor%20states%20with%20lower%20population%20density%2C%20from%20the%20mountainous%20terrains%20of%20Montana%20and%20Idaho%20to%20the%20plains%20of%20Kansas%20and%20Nebraska.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20part%20of%20what's%20driving%20Gen%20Zers%20to%20these%20states%20is%20the%20acceptance%20of%20remote%20work%2C%20more%20affordable%20homes%2C%20and%20the%20closeness%20to%20outdoor%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20RentCafe%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rentcafe.com%2Fblog%2Frental-market%2Fmarket-snapshots%2Fmillennials-switch-renter-to-owner-majority%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20homeowners%20totaled%202%20million%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20Gen%20X%20and%20millennial%20homeowners%20totaled%2024.4%20million%20and%2018.2%20million%2C%20respectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20older%20generations%20are%20holding%20onto%20their%20homes%20as%20interest%20rates%20stay%20high%2C%20leading%20Gen%20Zers%20to%20find%20new%20places%20to%20live%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20supply%20and%20affordability%2C%20Doug%20Ressler%2C%20the%20business%20intelligence%20manager%20at%20Yardi%20Matrix%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20Gen%20Z%20can't%20get%20into%20the%20housing%20market%20in%20popular%20cities%20%E2%80%94%20in%20both%20buying%20and%20renting%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20casting%20a%20wider%20net%20in%20their%20home%20search%2C%20Ressler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20the%20Gen%20Zers%20be%20more%20movement%20oriented%2C%20especially%20in%20long%20distances%2C%26quot%3B%20Ressler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20determine%20the%20number%20of%20Gen%20Z%20movers%2C%20which%20it%20limited%20to%20those%20aged%2018%20to%2023%2C%20StorageCafe%20analyzed%202021%20data%20from%20the%20Census%20Bureau's%20American%20Community%20Survey%20Public%20Use%20Microdata%20Sample.%20It%20also%20used%20the%20Census%20data%20to%20determine%20the%20median%20value%20of%20owner-occupied%20housing.%20For%20rent%20values%2C%20it%20relied%20on%20data%20from%20Yardi%20Matrix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%2010%20states%20where%20Gen%20Zers%20are%20migrating%20to%2C%20according%20to%20StorageCafe%2C%20ranked%20by%20percentage%20of%20total%20newcomers%20who%20identify%20as%20members%20of%20that%20generation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E10.%20Indiana%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222222%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sunset%20on%20a%20main%20street%20in%20Indiana.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65328ed0be9edfa8eda5d81d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMadison%2C%20Indiana.%3Cp%3Elarrybraunphotography.com%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGen%20Z%20percentage%20of%20total%20move-ins%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2013%25%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20who%20moved%20to%20the%20state%20in%202021%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E109%2C271%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHome%20value%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%24182%2C338%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAverage%20rent%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%241%2C229%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnemployment%20rate%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E3.2%25%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E9.%20Nebraska%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221779%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22omaha%20nebraska%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d3626d836e03c588e14c64c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOmaha%2C%20Nebraska.%3