er.com%2F6535d9c40487ff031cab6f69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BWe%20welcome%20business%20with%20China%2C%20visitors%20from%20China%2C%20academic%20exchange.%20What%20we%20don't%20welcome%20is%20cheating%2C%20and%20theft%2C%20and%20repression%2C%26quot%3B%20Christopher%20Wray%20told%2060%20Minutes'%20Scott%20Pelley.%3Cp%3EMark%20Wilson%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Zhang%20Tao%2FXinhua%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EFBI%20chief%20Christopher%20Wray%20says%20China%20is%20running%20the%20world's%20largest%20hacking%20program.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHe%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fchina-stealing-technology-secrets-five-eyes-intelligence-leaders-warn-60-minutes-transcript%2F%5C%22%3E60%20Minutes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20China%20has%20stolen%20more%20US%20data%20%26quot%3Bthan%20every%20nation%2C%20big%20or%20small%2C%20combined.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EWray%20said%20China's%20espionage%20work%20could%20threaten%20the%20competitiveness%20of%20the%20US%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFBI%20Director%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-director-somewhat-insane-to-suggest-hes-biased-against-conservatives-2023-7%5C%22%3EChristopher%20Wray%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20China%20is%20running%20the%20world's%20most%20extensive%20hacking%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20the%20biggest%20hacking%20program%20in%20the%20world%20by%20far%2C%20bigger%20than%20ever%20other%20major%20nation%20combined.%20Stolen%20more%20of%20our%20personal%20and%20corporate%20data%20than%20every%20nation%2C%20big%20or%20small%2C%20combined%2C%26quot%3B%20Wray%20told%2060%20Minutes'%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fteam%2Fscott-pelley%2F%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%226c40e26aa045a6279bc373c155ba943a%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2260%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fteam%2Fscott-pelley%2F%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScott%20Pelley%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fchina-stealing-technology-secrets-five-eyes-intelligence-leaders-warn-60-minutes-transcript%2F%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20aired%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWray%20was%20speaking%20during%20a%20joint%20interview%20with%20his%20counterparts%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dni.gov%2Findex.php%2Fncsc-how-we-work%2F217-about%2Forganization%2Ficig-pages%2F2660-icig-fiorc%5C%22%3EFive%20Eyes%3C%2Fa%3E%20intelligence%20alliance%2C%20a%20grouping%20that%20consists%20of%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Canada%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWray%20told%20Pelley%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-spy-case-shows-how-industrial-espionage-helps-chinese-military-2021-12%5C%22%3EChina's%20intelligence%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20poses%20a%20significant%20threat%20to%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20is%20that%20when%20people%20talk%20about%20stealing%20innovation%20or%20intellectual%20property%2C%20that's%20not%20just%20a%20Wall%20Street%20problem.%20That's%20a%20Main%20Street%20problem.%20That%20means%20American%20jobs%2C%20American%20families%2C%20American%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20the%20same%20thing%20for%20every%20one%20of%20our%20five%20countries%2C%20directly%20impacted%20by%20that%20theft%2C%26quot%3B%20Wray%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20some%20abstract%20concept.%20It%20has%20flesh%20and%20blood%2C%20kitchen-table%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Wray%20stopped%20short%20of%20saying%20that%20China%20is%20engaging%20in%20criminal%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20seem%20to%20be%20saying%20that%20the%20Chinese%20government%20is%20running%20a%20criminal%20enterprise%2C%26quot%3B%20Pelley%20told%20Wray%20during%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20I%20would%20say%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20if%20they%20want%20to%20be%20a%20great%20nation%2C%20it's%20time%20for%20them%20to%20start%20acting%20like%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20Wray%20said%20in%20response%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Chinese%20government%20should%20work%20with%20other%20countries%20to%20combat%20common%20threats%20like%20drug%20trafficking%20and%20money%20laundering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20means%20not%20working%20with%20criminals%20but%20rather%20working%20to%20uphold%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%2060%20Minutes%2C%20China%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bfirmly%20oppose%20the%20groundless%20allegations%20and%20smears%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20news%20program's%20interviewees.%2060%20Minutes%20did%20not%20specify%20which%20of%20China's%20ministries%20or%20agencies%20provided%20the%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20been%20fending%20off%20China's%20attempts%20at%20espionage.%20In%20February%2C%20the%20US%20military%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-spy-balloon-synthetic-aperture-radar-discord-documents-pentagon-2023-4%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22fd05cb24adc34b07f1cc3223b54c4475%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-spy-balloon-synthetic-aperture-radar-discord-documents-pentagon-2023-4%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%3Eshot%20down%20a%20Chinese%20surveillance%20balloon%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20it%20flew%20over%20the%20continental%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fcuba-to-host-secret-chinese-spy-base-focusing-on-u-s-b2fed0e0%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%226cef689b6ede2723bdca529503c