_articleshow%2F104644727.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-hamas-war-egypt-is-courted-on-all-sides-as-pivotal-to-gaza-refugees-fate%2Famp_articleshow%2F104644727.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala%20Temple%20Board%20Says%20No%20to%20RSS%20Drills%2C%20Training%20on%20Temple%20Premises%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23122455%2FTemple_in_Kerala.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Travancore%20Devaswom%20Board%20(TDB)%20has%20asked%20all%20temples%20under%20its%20control%20to%20not%20allow%20mass%20drills%20or%20any%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fthiruvananthapuram%2Fno-rss-drills-on-temple-premises-tdb%2Farticleshow%2F100438945.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eactivities%20organised%20by%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%3C%2Fa%3E%20(RSS)%20on%20their%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20restriction%20is%20already%20in%20place%2C%20the%20board%20issued%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fthiruvananthapuram%2Fno-rss-drills-on-temple-premises-tdb%2Farticleshow%2F100438945.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Efresh%20directive%20reiterating%20the%20ban%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20reports%20of%20RSS%20activities%20happening%20in%20a%20few%20temples%20in%20Kerala%20surfaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20circular%20issued%20by%20the%20board%20clarified%20that%20other%20than%20temple%20festivals%20and%20rituals%2C%20the%20premises%20should%20not%20be%20used%20for%20other%20purposes%20and%20officers%20who%20fail%20to%20comply%20with%20this%20order%20may%20face%20strict%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%20(LDF)%20government%20had%20expressed%20their%20opposition%20to%20RSS%20using%20temple%20premises%20for%20their%20physical%20training%20that%20sometimes%20involve%20weapons.%20Chief%20minister%20Pinrayi%20Vijayan%