derabad-hindutva-profile%5C%22%3EHow%20Raja%20Singh%20of%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20Goshamahal%20Emerged%20as%20the%20New%20Poster%20Boy%20of%20Hindutva%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Hyderabad%20police%20in%20August%20under%20the%20Preventive%20Detention%20Act%20for%20hurting%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20the%20minority%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Telangana%20high%20court%20released%20him%20while%20laying%20down%20three%20strict%20conditions.%C2%A0Justices%20A.%20Abhishek%20Reddy%20and%20Juvvadi%20Sridevi%20said%20he%20%E2%80%9Cshall%20not%20participate%20in%20or%20hold%20any%20celebratory%20rallies%2Fmeetings%20after%20his%20release%E2%80%9D%3B%20shall%20be%20prohibited%20from%20giving%20%E2%80%9Cany%20interviews%20to%20any%20kind%20of%20media%20houses%20including%20the%20print%20media%E2%80%9D%3B%20and%20%E2%80%9Cshall%20not%20make%20any%20provocative%20speeches%20against%20any%20religion%20or%20post%20any%20derogatory%20or%20offensive%20posts%20on%20any%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20Facebook%2C%20Twitter%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20YouTube%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%2C%20he%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fraja-singh-court-restrictions-violence-muslims%5C%22%3Eviolated%3C%2Fa%3E%20these%20conditions%20more%20than%20once%20and%20has%20made%20hate%20speeches%20on%20several%20occassions.%20He%20has%2C%20however%2C%20not%20been%20arrested%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698043521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F07134553%2Fraja-singh.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bjp-suspension-t-raja-singh-comments-prophet-muhammad%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Telangana's%20assembly%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20on%20November%2030%20and%20Singh%2C%20who%20has%20over%2010