-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-international-airlines-cancels-flights-over-non-payment-of-dues-to-fuel-supplier%2Famp_articleshow%2F104643154.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-international-airlines-cancels-flights-over-non-payment-of-dues-to-fuel-supplier%2Famp_articleshow%2F104643154.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20food%20inflation%20back%20to%20haunt%20the%20Indian%20economy%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698043000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104643125%2Cimgsize-128166.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fis-food-inflation-back-to-haunt-the-indian-economy%2Farticleshow%2F104643086.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20recent%20good%20news%20is%20that%20vegetable%20price%20pressure%20has%20eased%2C%20with%20inflation%20dropping%20from%20its%20July%20peak%20of%2037.4%25%20to%203.4%25%20in%20September%2C%20thanks%20to%20increased%20supplies.%20However%2C%20onion%20prices%20continue%20to%20pose%20a%20challenge%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20of%20vegetable%20prices%20rising%20again%2C%20CRISIL%20cautions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fis-food-inflation-back-to-haunt-the-indian-economy%2Farticleshow%2F104643086.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bipasha%20visits%20Durga%20Puja%20with%20Devi%20and%20Karan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698042623000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104642901%2Cimgsize-21180.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbipasha-basu-looks-elegant-in-a-saree-as-she-visits-durga-puja-pandal-with-baby-devi-and-hubby-karan-singh-grover-watch%2Farticleshow%2F104642901.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104642901.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBipasha%20was%20elegantly%20dressed%20in%20a%20green%20saree%2C%20paired%20with%20a%20pink-coloured%20blouse%20and%20she%20dressed%20up%20their%2011-month-old%20daughter%2C%20Devi%2C%20in%20an%20adorable%20rani%20pink%20saree.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbipasha-basu-looks-elegant-in-a-saree-as-she-visits-durga-puja-pandal-with-baby-devi-and-hubby-karan-singh-grover-watch%2Farticleshow%2F104642901.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20Settlers%20Are%20Using%20the%20Ongoing%20Violence%20to%20Ethnically%20Cleanse%20Palestinians%20in%20Jordan%20Valley%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23110534%2FJordan_Valley_%25D8%25BA%25D9%2588%25D8%25B1_%25D8%25A7%25D9%2584%25D8%25A7%25D9%2594%25D8%25B1%25D8%25AF%25D9%2586_-_panoramio_1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fspeeches-remarks%2F2023%2F10%2F10%2Fremarks-by-president-biden-on-the-terrorist-attacks-in-israel-2%2F%5C%22%3Ewarned%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20speech%20on%20October%2010%2C%20regarding%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnyone%20thinking%20of%20taking%20advantage%20of%20this%20situation%2C%20I%20have%20one%20word%3A%20Don%E2%80%99t.%20Don%E2%80%99t.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20settlers%20in%20the%20Jordan%20Valley%20are%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20war%20with%20Hamas%20to%20accelerate%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20cleansing%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20shepherds%20and%20farmers%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20number%20of%20families%20that%20were%20forcibly%20evacuated%20(16)%20is%20not%20big%2C%20their%20transfer%20has%20a%20dramatic%20meaning%20since%20they%20were%20the%20last%20families%20of%20Palestinian%20farmers%20and%20shepherds%20who%20survived%20until%20now%20in%20the%20area.%20Their%20transfer%2C%20and%20also%20the%20expected%20transfer%20of%20other%20families%20who%20are%20being%20subjected%20to%20similar%20violent%20pressure%20by%20the%20settlers%2C%20will%20leave%20a%20large%20area%20of%20the%20Jordan%20Valley%20without%20any%20Palestinian%20farmers%20and%20shepherds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20targets%20of%20the%20accelerated%20ethnic%20cleansing%20who%20were%20chosen%20since%20October%207%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20Palestinian%20communities%20in%20all%20of%20the%20West%20Bank.%20The%20communities%20of%20Palestinian%20shepherds%20and%20farmers%20in%20the%20Jordan%20Valley%20already%20have%20been%20suffering%20from%20the%20severe%20impact%20of%20decades%20of%20illegal%20Israeli%20occupation%2C%20from%20the%20policies%20of%20ethnic%20cleansing%20and%20apartheid%20by%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20in%20the%20Jordan%20Valley%2C%20and%20from%20the%20systematic%20and%20widespread%20violations%20of%20their%20rights%20that%20are%20recognised%20in%20the%20core%20humanitarian%20law%20treaties.%20These%20illegal%20policies%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20caused%20high%20rates%20of%20poverty%2C%20food%20insecurity%2C%20inadequate%20water%20supply%20and%20unsafe%20drinking%20water%2C%20lack%20of%20electricity%2C%20fuel%20and%20medical%20and%20education%20services.%20They%20had%20no%20way%20to%20survive%20other%20than%20grazing%20their%20herds%20and%20farming%20their%20lands.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20several%20years%2C%20settlers%20established%20new%20%E2%80%9Cshepherd%20farms%E2%80%9D%20through%20violence%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Israeli%20military%20and%20police%2C%20and%20managed%20to%20take%20control%20of%20many%20of%20the%20last%20grazing%20and%20agricultural%20areas%20that%20were%20available%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20settlers%20by%20themselves%20or%20with%20the%20help%20of%20their%20accomplices%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.middleeastmonitor.com%2F20230808-us-activists-call-for-blacklisting-of-israeli-settler-hilltop-youths%2F%5C%22%3EHilltop%20Youth%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20violently%20prevented%20the%20Palestinian%20shepherds%20and%20farmers%20from%20grazing%20and%20cultivating%20their%20lands.%20This%20was%20done%20almost%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20by%20harassing%2C%20attacking%20and%20threatening%20them%2C%20and%20also%20by%20harassing%2C%20attacking%20and%20threatening%20the%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20activists%20who%20accompany%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20settlers%E2%80%99%20methods%20through%20the%20years%20were%20throwing%20stones%20at%20the%20herds%20and%20at%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20driving%20vehicles%20or%20riding%20horses%20within%20the%20herds%20and%20cultivated%20fields%2C%20sending%20low-flying%20noisy%20drones%20to%20frighten%20and%20disperse%20the%20herds%2C%20setting%20attack%20dogs%20on%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20their%20herds%2C%20whipping%20the%20herds%20and%20the%20Palestinians%20with%20sticks%20or%20whips%2C%20beating%20and%20pushing%20them%2C%20burning%20or%20threatening%20to%20burn%20the%20pastures%2C%20threatening%20to%20stab%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20conducting%20uninvited%20threatening%20%E2%80%9Cvisits%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20Palestinians%E2%80%99%20residences.%20As%20a%20result%20of%20the%20violent%20dispersal%20of%20the%20herds%2C%20some%20sheep%20miscarry%2C%20stop%20giving%20milk%2C%20run%20and%20break%20their%20legs%20or%20get%20sick%20and%20some%20are%20even%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20First%20Sights%20and%20Sounds%20of%20War%3A%20Notes%20from%20Israel-Palestine%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-diary-gaza-occupation%5C%22%3EThe%20First%20Sights%20and%20Sounds%20of%20War%3A%20Notes%20from%20Israel-Palestine%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20and%20police%20act%20in%20the%20Jordan%20Valley%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20settlers%E2%80%99%20instructions%2C%20arresting%20or%20evicting%20the%20Palestinians%20from%20their%20cultivated%20and%20grazing%20lands%20and%20thus%20assisting%20in%20the%20settlers%E2%80%99%20takeover.%20In%20many%20incidents%20the%20soldiers%20and%20policemen%20were%20present%20during%20the%20settlers%E2%80%99%20violence%20against%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20lift%20a%20finger%20to%20stop%20it.%20Also%2C%20in%20many%20incidents%20the%20soldiers%20and%20policemen%20arrest%20the%20Palestinian%20shepherds%20and%20farmers%20who%20dare%20to%20complain%20against%20the%20settlers.%20Many%20times%2C%20when%20Israeli%20soldiers%20and%20policemen%20detained%20the%20Palestinian%20shepherds%2C%20their%20herds%20were%20left%20alone%20and%20dispersed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20October%207%2C%20the%20settlers%20increased%20their%20chokehold%20on%20these%20Palestinian%20farmers%E2%80%99%20and%20shepherds%E2%80%99%20communities%2C%20and%20finally%20managed%20to%20force%20them%20to%20leave%20their%20families%E2%80%99%20homes%20and%20lands.%20This%20was%20done%20through%20increasing%20physical%20violence%20and%20also%20by%20repeated%20%E2%80%9Cvisits%E2%80%9D%20of%20armed%20settlers%20in%20their%20residential%20compounds%20where%20the%20settlers%20ordered%20them%20to%20evacuate%20immediately%20and%20threatened%20that%20if%20they%20did%20not%20evacuate%20on%20their%20own%2C%20they%20would%20evict%20them%20forcibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEthnic%20cleansing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fgenocideprevention%2Fethnic-cleansing.shtml%5C%22%3Ehas%20not%3C%2Fa%3E%20been%20recognised%20as%20an%20independent%20crime%20under%20international%20law%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20precise%20definition%20of%20this%20concept%20or%20the%20exact%20acts%20to%20be%20qualified%20as%20ethnic%20cleansing.%20A%20United%20Nations%20Commission%20of%20Experts%2C%20mandated%20to%20look%20into%20violations%20of%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20committed%20in%20the%20territory%20of%20the%20former%20Yugoslavia%2C%20defined%20ethnic%20cleansing%20in%20its%20interim%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fundocs.org%2FHome%2FMobile%3FFinalSymbol%3DS%252F25274%26Language%3DE%26DeviceType%3DDesktop%26LangRequested%3DFalse%5C%22%3ES%2F25274%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%C2%A0rendering%20an%20area%20ethnically%20homogeneous%20by%20using%20force%20or%20intimidation%20to%20remove%20persons%20of%20given%20groups%20from%20the%20area.%E2%80%9D%20In%20its%20final%20report%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fundocs.org%2FHome%2FMobile%3FFinalSymbol%3DS%252F1994%252F674%26Language%3DE%26DeviceType%3DDesktop%26LangRequested%3DFalse%5C%22%3ES%2F1994%2F674%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20same%20Commission%20described%20ethnic%20cleansing%20as%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20a%20purposeful%20policy%20designed%20by%20one%20ethnic%20or%20religious%20group%20to%20remove%20by%20violent%20and%20terror-inspiring%20means%20the%20civilian%20population%20of%20another%20ethnic%20or%20religious%20group%20from%20certain%20geographic%20areas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20why%20the%20international%20community%20and%20the%20international%20criminal%20courts%20rely%20on%20the%20recognised%20crime%20of%20forced%20transfer%20of%20a%20population%2C%20that%20is%20defined%20as%20a%20war%20crime%20or%20a%20crime%20against%20humanity.%20For%20example%2C%20Article%2049%20of%20the%20Fourth%20Geneva%20Convention%20relative%20to%20the%20Protection%20of%20Civilian%20Persons%20in%20Time%20of%20War%20(1949)%20forbids%20the%20forced%20transfer%20of%20protected%20persons%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20occupied%20territory%20or%20to%20the%20area%20of%20the%20occupying%20power%20itself%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20settling%20of%20residents%20of%20the%20occupying%20power%20inside%20the%20occupied%20territory.%20Articles%20146-147%20define%20the%20forced%20transfer%20of%20protected%20inhabitants%20as%20a%20serious%20violation%20of%20the%20convention.%20Also%2C%20Articles%207(2)(d)%20and%208(2)(b)(%20viii)%20of%20the%20Rome%20Statute%20of%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20(1998)%20define%20as%20a%20war%20crime%20or%20a%20crime%20against%20humanity%20the%20deportation%20or%20forcible%20transfer%20of%20population.%20It%20should%20be%20emphasised%20that%20the%20United%20States%20has%20long%20recognised%20%E2%80%9Cethnic%20cleansing%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20war%20crime.%20For%20example%2C%20regarding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Freports-of-mass-atrocities-in-western-tigray%2F%5C%22%3EEthiopia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kosovo%2C%20Bosnia%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fit.usembassy.gov%2Fsecretary-blinken-remarks-on-the-release-of-the-2021-wiesel-report%2F%5C%22%3EMyanmar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Let%20Us%20Not%20Forget%20What%20Made%20Hamas%20and%20Caused%20the%20Recent%20Eruption%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Flet-us-not-forget-what-made-hamas-and-caused-the-recent-eruption%5C%22%3ELet%20Us%20Not%20Forget%20What%20Made%20Hamas%20and%20Caused%20the%20Recent%20Eruption%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20the%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20organisations%20and%20movements%20%E2%80%93%20Bimkom%20%E2%80%93%20Planners%20for%20Planning%20Rights%2C%20Combatants%20for%20Peace%2C%20Ir%20Amim%2C%20Jordan%20Valley%20Activists%2C%20Machsom%20Watch%2C%20Mothers%20Against%20Violence%2C%20Other%20Voice%2C%20Psychoactive%2C%20Torat%20Tzedek%20an%20Zochrot%20%E2%80%93%20which%20support%20and%20accompany%20the%20communities%20of%20Palestinian%20shepherds%20and%20farmers%20in%20the%20Jordan%20Valley%2C%20asked%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20EU%20to%20demand%20from%20the%20Israeli%20government%20to%20stop%20the%20accelerated%20ethnic%20cleansing%20carried%20out%20these%20days%20by%20the%20settlers%20in%20the%20Jordan%20Valley%2C%20to%20allow%20the%20communities%20that%20have%20been%20deported%20since%20October%207%20to%20return%20to%20their%20homes%20and%20lands%20after%20giving%20guarantees%20for%20their%20security%2C%20and%20urgently%20enforce%20their%20Magnitsky%20Acts%20and%20include%20the%20settlers%20in%20their%20list%20of%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20to%20us%20that%20the%20Israeli%20government%20has%20no%20interest%20in%20acting%20on%20its%20own%20initiative%20since%20it%20wishes%20to%20complete%20the%20annexation%20of%20the%20area%20de%20facto%20and%20de%20jure.%20The%20same%20violent%20pressure%20is%20being%20used%20against%20other%20Palestinian%20shepherds%20and%20farmers%20communities%20in%20the%20Jordan%20Valley.%20If%20the%20settlers%20succeed%20in%20their%20plan%20there%20could%20be%20an%20almost%20complete%20ethnic%20cleansing%20of%20the%20Jordan%20Valley%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20large%20Palestinian%20towns%20and%20cities%20such%20as%20Jericho%20and%20Bardala.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEitay%20Mack%20is%20a%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20and%20activist%20based%20in%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698042613000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23110534%2FJordan_Valley_%25D8%25BA%25D9%2588%25D8%25B1_%25D8%25A7%25D9%2584%25D8%25A7%25D9%2594%25D8%25B1%25D8%25AF%25D9%2586_-_panoramio_1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraeli-settlers-are-using-the-ongoing-violence-to-ethnically-cleanse-palestinians-in-jordan-valley%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20targets%20of%20the%20accelerated%20ethnic%20cleansing%20who%20were%20chosen%20since%20October%207%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20Palestinian%20com