3EBloomberg%20reported%20the%20company's%20lag%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20is%20considered%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3Bpretty%20big%20miss%20internally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETo%20catch%20up%2C%20the%20company%20is%20planning%20updates%20to%20Siri%20that%20incorporate%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-airtag-dozens-more-stalking-victims-join-lawsuit-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20working%20toward%20releasing%20a%20new%20version%20of%20Siri%20that%20incorporates%20AI%20technology%20after%20a%20quieter%20start%20with%20large%20language%20models%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecompared%20to%20its%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20Senior%20Vice%20Presidents%20John%20Giannandrea%20and%20Craig%20Federighi%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20in%20charge%20of%20AI%20and%20software%20engineering%20%E2%80%94%20are%20overseeing%20the%20AI%20developments%20at%20the%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Fnewsletters%2F2023-10-22%2Fwhat-is-apple-doing-in-ai-revamping-siri-search-apple-music-and-other-apps-lo1ffr7p%3FleadSource%3Duverify%2520wall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20Bloomberg's%20reporting%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiannandrea's%20team%20is%20developing%20new%20AI%20systems.%20His%20employees%20are%20reworking%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmarter%20%26quot%3B%20Siri%20that%20uses%20them%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%20The%20new%20Siri%20could%20launch%20as%20soon%20as%20next%20year%20but%20may%20take%20longer%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederighi's%20team%20is%20also%20working%20hard%20to%20add%20AI%20to%20the%20subsequent%20versions%20of%20iOS%2C%20which%20should%20allow%20for%20improved%20response%20and%20auto-completion%20components%20to%20both%20Siri%20and%20the%20Messages%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20teams%20work%2C%20other%20internal%20debates%20have%20been%20raging%20about%20whether%20generative%20AI%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bon-d