%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20if%20the%20BJP%20(Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party)%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20give%20me%20a%20ticket%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Bhawani%20Singh%20Rajawat%2C%20a%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20loyalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Kota%20Ladpura%20seat%20is%20a%20stronghold%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Rajawat%20served%20as%20the%20MLA%20from%20this%20constituency%20between%202003%20and%202018%2C%20until%20the%20BJP%20denied%20him%20a%20ticket.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20Ijyaraj%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20a%20Congress%20MP%20from%20the%20Kota-Bundi%20seat%2C%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Kalpana%20Devi%2C%20was%20given%20the%20ticket%20from%20Ladpura.%20Rajawat%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20received%20votes%20using%20my%20name%3B%20the%20seeds%20that%20I%20had%20sown%20were%20producing%20the%20fruits%20of%20labour%20that%20she%20reaped.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Hadoti%20area%20has%2017%20seats%2C%20with%2010%20held%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20seven%20by%20the%20Congress.%20Two%20MPs%2C%20both%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20represent%20this%20region%3A%20Lok%20Sabha%20speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20Dushyant%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20have%20yet%20to%20announce%20their%20candidates%20for%20the%20Ladpura%20seat.%20Both%20parties%20have%20released%20two%20lists%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajawat%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20phone%20on%20the%20future%20of%20his%20political%20career%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Edited%20excerpts%20from%20the%20conversation%20are%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20recently%20met%20former%20chief%20minister%20Vasundhara%20Raje.%20Did%20you%20discuss%20the%20possibility%20of%20receiving%20a%20ticket%20this%20time%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20met%20with%20Ms%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20five%20days%20ago%2C%20and%20she%20assured%20me%20that%20she%20is%20working%20on%20securing%20my%20ticket.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20I%20will%20receive%20the%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20two%20examples%20in%20Jaipur%20where%20close%20aides%20of%20Raje%E2%80%99s%20didn%E2%80%99t%20receive%20tickets.%20How%20do%20you%20view%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20all%20party%20workers%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20about%20proximity%20to%20someone.%20Others%20who%20received%20tickets%20are%20also%20dedicated%20party%20workers.%20I%20believe%20the%20party%20is%20functioning%20with%20Vasundhara-ji%2C%20and%20she%20has%20not%20been%20sidelined.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20assess%20your%20party%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20from%202013%20to%202018%20under%20Raje%E2%80%99s%20leadership%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20administrations%20I%E2%80%99ve%20witnessed%20since%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%2C%20led%20by%20Raje.%20We%20achieved%20a%20mandate%20of%20163%20seats%20during%20her%20leadership%2C%20and%20those%20were%20years%20of%20significant%20development%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20it%20was%20the%20best%20regime%20under%20Raje%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20why%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20party%20declared%20her%20as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20will%20decide%20who%20becomes%20the%20chief%20minister%20after%20winning%20the%20election%2C%20and%20we%20have%20no%20objections%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision%20on%20that%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20think%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20sideline%20Raje%20because%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20align%20with%20the%20current%20politics%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20may%20not%20be%20rooted%20in%20communal%20politics%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVasundhara-ji%20is%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20leader%2C%20and%20everyone%20respects%20her.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20the%20party%20is%20attempting%20to%20sideline%20her%3B%20she%20is%20invited%20to%20every%20party%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%202018%20elections%2C%20do%20you%20think%20Kalpana%20Devi%2C%20who%20contested%20from%20your%20seat%2C%20received%20votes%20and%20won%20because%20of%20your%20support%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20the%20support%20base%20was%20primarily%20mine%2C%20which%20contributed%20to%20her%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20see%20the%20role%20Om%20Birla%20in%20your%20ticket%20being%20given%20to%20Kalpana%20Devi%2C%20considering%20that%20her%20husband%20was%20a%20contender%20to%20him%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20in%202018%2C%20Raje%20asked%20me%20to%20compromise%20on%20the%20seat%2C%20as%20%3Cem%3Eraj%20pariwar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BIjyraj%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20family%20is%20locally%20referred%20to%20as%20royalty%5D%20was%20joining%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20will%20you%20do%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20receive%20a%20ticket%3F%20Would%20you%20consider%20joining%20the%20Congress%20if%20they%20offer%20you%20a%20ticket%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20would%20consider%20taking%20a%20chance%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20but%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20the%20party%20%5BBJP%5D%20will%20not%20let%20me%20down%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698032256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23085424%2F305266608_5363998863635219_8570448002052232742_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwill-consider-congress-ticket-if-bjp-doesnt-give-one-vasundhara-raje-loyalist-bhawani-singh-rajawat%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajawat%20served%20as%20the%20MLA%20from%20Kota%20Ladpura%20between%202003%20and%202018%2C%20until%20the%20BJP%20denied%20him%20a%20ticket.%20He%20spoke%20to%20The%20Wire%20about%20the%20future%20of%20his%20political%20career%20with%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagem