78.html%5C%22%3EPakistani%20rupee%20plunging%20against%20the%20US%20dollar%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20sapped%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20purchasing%20power%2C%20making%20it%20highly%20unpopular.%20Sitting%20atop%20the%20coalition%2C%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20squandered%20the%20PML-N%E2%80%99s%20political%20capital%20by%20the%20fistfuls%20and%20was%20petrified%20of%20elections.%20But%20with%20Imran%20Khan%20training%20his%20guns%20on%20the%20incumbent%20COAS%20General%20Asim%20Munir%2C%20the%20top%20brass%20and%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20held%20each%20other%20in%20an%20ever%20tighter%20embrace.%20This%20nexus%2C%20however%2C%20deprived%20the%20PML-N%20of%20its%20anti-establishment%20credentials%2C%20which%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20had%20buttressed%20since%20his%20ouster.%20Bereft%20both%20of%20performance%20and%20a%20political%20plank%2C%20the%20PML-N%20dreaded%20to%20face%20a%20resurgent%20Imran%20Khan%20at%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20approval%20taking%20a%20plunge%20and%20faced%20still%20with%20a%20myriad%20legal%20battles%20at%20home%2C%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20kept%20deferring%20his%20return.%20But%20after%20landing%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20the%20army%20establishment%2C%20Imran%20Khan%20faced%20his%20own%20legal%20problems%2C%20though%20the%20judiciary%20still%20gave%20him%20preferential%20treatment.%20All%20that%2C%20however%2C%20when%20the%20protesting%20PTI%20leaders%20and%20cadres%2C%20most%20likely%20under%20instructions%20from%20Imran%20Khan%20himself%2C%20made%20the%20monumental%20blunder%20of%20attacking%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nation.com.pk%2F10-May-2023%2Fghq-attacked-lahore-corps-commander-house-set-on-fire-by-pti-protesters%5C%22%3Earmy%E2%80%99s%20GHQ%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-pti-imran-khan-protests-violence%5C%22%3Eother%20installations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1751782%2Fimran-khan-arrested-from-ihc-court-deems-ex-pms-arrest-legal%5C%22%3Ehis%20arrest%3C%2Fa%3E%20finally%20came%20about.%20Overnight%2C%20Imran%20Khan%20went%20from%20being%20a%20political%20martyr%20to%20a%20dead%20man%20walking.%20A%20furious%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-army-imran-khan-scorned%5C%22%3Ebrass%20cracked%20its%20whip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20rounding%20up%20hundreds%20of%20PTI%20men%20and%20women.%20Imran%20Khan%20himself%20was%20rearrested%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F9%2F27%2Fpakistan-ex-pm-imran-khan-moved-to-another-jail-after-custody-extended%5C%22%3Eremains%20incarcerated%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20was%20not%20enough.%20The%20army%20under%20General%20Asim%20Munir%20put%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20party%20on%20the%20chopping%20block%20to%20degrade%20its%20electoral%20capabilities.%20Defections%20and%20break%20away%20factions%20were%20induced%20and%20even%20a%20new%20party%20was%20carved%20out%20of%20the%20PTI.%20Instead%20of%20recapturing%20any%20ground%20from%20the%20army%2C%20the%20Shehbaz%20Sharif-led%20coalition%20abjectly%20abdicated%20the%20political%20and%20governance%20space%20to%20the%20junta.%20By%20giving%20constitutional%20and%20legal%20cover%20to%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20business%20enterprises%20and%20unbridled%20internal%20security%20authority%2C%20the%20outgoing%20government%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20an%20Indonesian-style%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-full-blown-praetorian-state-shehbaz-sharif-imran-khan%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDwifungsi%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%E2%80%9Cdual%20function%E2%80%9D%20military%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20that%20still%20did%20not%20solve%20the%20popularity%20issue%20for%20the%20next%20general%20elections%2C%20as%20the%20economy%20continued%20to%20be%20measly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20PML-N%20wanted%20its%20leader%20back%20in%20the%20saddle.%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20for%20his%20part%2C%20though%20not%20shy%20of%20facing%20the%20c