20of%20the%20carnival%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20permitted%20to%20continue%20their%20sit-in%20protest.%20However%2C%20on%20the%20remaining%20364%20days%20of%20the%20year%2C%20a%20few%20of%20them%20will%20still%20be%20found%20on%20the%20streets.%20This%20site%20has%20ingrained%20itself%20as%20a%20part%20of%20Kolkata%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20their%20struggles%20are%20often%20overlooked%20or%20forgotten%20by%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20still%20in%20shock%20by%20how%20the%20government%20overlooked%20qualified%20and%20talented%20students%20in%20favour%20of%20recruiting%20others.%20The%20entire%20system%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20rigged%2C%20and%20those%20behind%20the%20manipulation%20of%20OMR%20sheets%20have%20already%20been%20apprehended%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Karim%20Shekh%2C%20who%20cleared%20the%20examination%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fkolkata%2Frecruitment-scam-calcutta-hc-cancels-appointment-of-teachers-8606158%2F%5C%22%3Erecruitment%20scandal%3C%2Fa%3E%20dates%20back%20to%202014%2C%20when%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Board%20of%20Primary%20Education%20conducted%20the%20teacher%20eligibility%20test%20(TET)%20for%20recruiting%20primary%20school%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20it%20came%20to%20light%20that%20individuals%20with%20low%20TET%20scores%20were%20granted%20teaching%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20are%20probing%20the%20matter%2C%20implicating%20several%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fed-raids-bengal-ministers-partha-chatterjee-paresh-adhikari%5C%22%3Eincluding%20former%20education%20minister%20Partha%20Chatterjee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20manipulate%20TET%20results%20through%20bribery%20and%20the%20hiring%20of%20ineligible%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20con