har%20is%20spending%20Durga%20Puja%20away%20from%20family%2C%20on%20the%20protest%20site.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20allow%20this%20to%20happen%20without%20any%20protest.%20Many%20schools%20are%20having%20very%20high%20PTR%20%5Bpupil-teacher%20ratio%5D%2C%20yet%20the%20eligible%20candidates%20are%20being%20denied%20jobs%20for%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20leaders%20from%20the%20Left%20parties%20have%20been%20visiting%20the%20protesters%20during%20the%20festive%20season.%20This%20year%2C%20CPI(M)%20state%20secretary%20Mohammed%20Salim%20and%20Democratic%20Youth%20Federation%20of%20India%20leader%20Minakshi%20Mukherjee%20met%20with%20them%20at%20the%20protest%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%2C%20however%2C%20brushed%20aside%20the%20gesture%2C%20alleging%20that%20they%20were%20politicising%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESushant%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20regular%20participant%20in%20the%20sit-in%20protest%2C%20expressed%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20court.%20Some%20illegal%20recruits%20have%20already%20lost%20their%20jobs%20for%20not%20providing%20proof%20of%20their%20qualifications.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CSurprisingly%2C%20the%20government%20is%20fighting%20for%20them%2C%20not%20thinking%20about%20us.%20We%E2%80%99re%20determined%20to%20persist%20until%20we%20get%20justice.%20Sadly%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20lost%20some%20of%20our%20comrades%20along%20the%20way%2C%20but%20we%20will%20continue%20our%20protest%20till%20we%20get%20our%20rightful%20job.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fbyline%2Faparna-bhattacharya%5C%22%3EAparna%20Bhattacharya%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697985893000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22194123%2F80a01b1a-b5fb-408c