d%20in%20the%20country%2C%20a%20total%20of%2014%2C965%20people%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20MP%20that%20year.%20The%20state%E2%80%99s%20suicide%20rate%20(17.8)%20was%20higher%20than%20the%20national%20average%20(12).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20September%202022%2C%20the%20state%20government%20constituted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmadhya-pradesh-government-to-prepare-a-draft-suicide-prevention-strategy%2Farticle65875268.ece%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ea%20task%20force%20committee%20to%20reduce%20the%20increasing%20cases%20of%20suicide%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20reacting%20to%20which%20the%20Congress%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20government%20had%20put%20up%20a%20show%20of%20opening%20%E2%80%98Anand%20Vibhag%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98Department%20of%20Happiness%E2%80%99%20and%20appointed%20many%20officials%20and%20employees%2C%20but%20its%20failure%20can%20be%20gauged%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20not%20only%20did%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20not%20feel%20happy%20but%2C%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20graph%20of%20suicides%20increased.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20in%202016%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20in%20the%20state%2C%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20had%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2FMadhya-Pradesh-becomes-first-State-to-have-%25E2%2580%2598Happiness-Department%25E2%2580%2599%2Farticle14491921.ece%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eapproved%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Happiness%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Broadly%20speaking%2C%20its%20basic%20objective%20was%20to%20measure%20the%20level%20of%20happiness%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20people%20and%20try%20to%20render%20happiness%20into%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20claimed%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20the%20National%20Happiness%20Index%20of%20Bhutan%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20it%20was%20also%20claimed%20that%20a%20%E2%80%98happiness%20index%E2%80%99%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20would%20also%20be%20released.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwhy-many-indians-dont-trust-mental-health-advice%5C%22%3EWhy%20Many%20Indians%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Trust%20Mental%20Health%20Advice%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20purpose%20of%20spreading%20happiness%20among%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%2C%20the%20government%20said%20that%20it%20would%20work%20with%20Isha%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Jaggi%20Vasudev%2C%20yoga%20guru%20and%20businessman%20Baba%20Ramdev%2C%20Avadheshanand%20and%20Sri%20Sri%20Ravi%20Shankar%2C%20and%20other%20such%20figures.%20With%20vigorous%20publicity%2C%20the%20Shivraj%20government%20had%20described%20MP%20as%20the%20first%20state%20in%20the%20country%20where%20such%20a%20department%20had%20been%20set%20up%20to%20fill%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%20with%20happiness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20department%20was%20headed%20by%20chief%20minister%20Chouhan%20himself.%20However%2C%20besides%20the%20officers%20deployed%20in%20the%20department%2C%20hardly%20anyone%20else%20in%20the%20state%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20progress%20made%20by%20this%20department%20after%20seven%20years%20of%20being%20established.%20To%20add%20to%20this%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98happiness%20index%E2%80%99%20has%20not%20been%20released%20even%20once.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20efforts%20of%20the%20department%20to%20spread%20happiness%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20department%20works%20through%20the%20state%20Anand%20Sansthan%2C%20which%20completely%20relies%20on%20volunteers%20or%20%E2%80%98anandaks%E2%80%99.%20The%20MP%20government%20has%20more%20than%2084%2C000%20anandaks%20registered%20with%20it.%20These%20anandaks%20assist%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20organisation%20and%20carry%20out%20any%20activities%20for%20the%20department%2C%20free%20of%20cost%2C%20alongside%20their%20own%20jobs%20or%20business.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnandaks%20are%20expected%20to%20set%20a%20positive%20example%20for%20others%20through%20their%20action%20and%20thoughts%20and%20inspire%20them%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20Anand%20Sansthan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20anandak%20can%20be%20a%20government%20servant%2C%20a%20private%20employee%20or%20self-employed.%20First%2C%20they%20have%20to%20get%20registered%20on%20the%20website%20after%20which%20the%20department%20provides%20them%20training%20on%20%E2%80%98how%20to%20lead%20a%20happy%20life%E2%80%99.%20After%20their%20life%20becomes%20%E2%80%98joyful%E2%80%99%20through%20this%20training%2C%20these%20people%2C%20as%20%E2%80%98anandam%20sahayogis%E2%80%99%2C%20are%20supposed%20to%20bring%20joy%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20other%20people%20of%20the%20society%2C%20motivate%20them%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20joyful%20activities%20of%20the%20department%20and%20also%20get%20them%20registered%20as%20fellow%20anandaks.%20An%20anandak%20can%20form%20an%20%E2%80%98Anand%20Club%E2%80%99%20by%20adding%20four%20more%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20its%20framework%2C%20the%20volunteers%20work%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20chain%20marketing%20and%20organise%20programs%20in%20their%20respective%20areas%20under%20the%20guidelines%20given%20by%20the%20happiness%20department%20for%20which%20they%20do%20not%20receive%20any%20kind%20of%20monetary%20assistance%20or%20honorarium.%20They%20have%20to%20do%20this%20work%20by%20taking%20time%20out%20from%20their%20respective%20jobs%20or%20business.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fnew-lens-mental-health-india-muslims-communalism-trauma%5C%22%3EStudy%20Says%20A%20New%20Lens%20Is%20Needed%20to%20Look%20at%20Mental%20Health%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20department%20organises%20%E2%80%98Anand%20Utsav%E2%80%99%20every%20year%20between%2014%20January%20and%2028%20January.%20According%20to%20the%20department%2C%20during%20this%20period%20events%20are%20organised%20in%20which%20people%20participate%20in%20performances%20like%20folk%20music%2C%20dance%2C%20singing%2C%20bhajan-kirtan%2C%20drama%20and%20sports%20activities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Anand%20Sabha%E2%80%99%20is%20organised%20in%20schools%20for%20students%20by%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20trained%20teachers%2C%20anandam%20associates%20and%20anandaks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20the%20department%20claims%20that%20it%20has%20set%20up%20172%20%E2%80%98Anandam%20Kendras%E2%80%99%20in%2052%20districts%20%E2%80%93%20also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Walls%20of%20Kindness%E2%80%99%20where%20people%20drop%20off%20unused%20items%20that%20anyone%20can%20take%20free%20of%20cost.%20It%20is%20also%20operated%20by%20anandaks%20but%20they%20are%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%98district%20contact%20person%E2%80%99%2C%20who%20can%20be%20a%20government%20servant%20or%20a%20non-government%20person.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Anand%20Shivirs%E2%80%99%20are%20organised%20to%20teach%20the%20government%20and%20non-government%20anandaks%20%E2%80%98how%20to%20live%20a%20fulfilling%20life%E2%80%99%20and%20to%20inculcate%20a%20positive%20attitude%20at%20three%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20Art%20of%20Living%20in%20Bengaluru%3B%20Initiative%20of%20Change%20in%20Pune%3B%20and%20Isha%20Foundation%20in%20Coimbatore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Work%20limited%20to%20website%20only%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20above%20information%20about%20departmental%20work%20available%20on%20the%20website%20may%20seem%20very%20appealing%2C%20but%20the%20ground%20reality%20is%20something%20else.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20spoke%20to%20several%20%E2%80%98anandam%20associates%E2%80%99.%20One%20such%20associate%2C%20Dr.%20Satya%20Prakash%20Sharma%2C%20is%20registered%20on%20the%20website%20as%20an%20%E2%80%98anandam%20sahayogi%E2%80%99%20from%20Gwalior.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%98Whatever%20exists%20(of%20the%20Anand%20Sansthan)%20is%20only%20on%20paper.%20On%20the%20ground%2C%20there%20is%20nothing.%20You%20will%20only%20get%20emails%20from%20the%20institute.%20Everything%20is%20on%20the%20website%2C%20nothing%20on%20the%20ground.%20The%20activity%20of%20the%20department%20is%20limited%20only%20to%20taking%20photographs%20and%20uploading%20them.%20Some%20events%20are%20organised%20by%20the%20department%20where%20photos%20are%20clicked%20and%20uploaded%20on%20the%20website.%20But%20other%20than%20that%20it%20is%20nothing%20more%20than%20just%20a%20website.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20get%20carried%20away%20just%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20website.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20scribe%20carried%20out%20a%20ground%20investigation%20of%20Dr.%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20claims%20and%20spoke%20to%20people%20from%20different%20sections%20of%20the%20state%20to%20know%20how%20they%20view%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Anand%20Department%E2%80%99%20and%20if%20they%20knew%20about%20its%20functioning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESocial%20worker%20Ajay%20Yadav%2C%20who%20is%20actively%20working%20on%20the%20issues%20of%20nutrition%2C%20health%2C%20education%2C%20employment%2C%20etc.%20among%20the%20tribal%20community%20in%20Shivpuri%20and%20Sheopur%20districts%2C%20is%20not%20even%20aware%20of%20the%20existence%20of%20any%20such%20department%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20working%20among%20the%20deprived%20sections%20for%20almost%20a%20decade%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20till%20date%20I%20have%20never%20heard%20the%20name%20of%20Anand%20Department%2C%20nor%20have%20I%20ever%20seen%20any%20event%20organised%20by%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fresearch-mental-health-caste%2F%5C%22%3EWe%20Need%20More%20Research%20on%20Mental%20Health%2C%20Caste%20and%20Religion%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESatish%20Rai%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Kewalari%20Kheda%20village%20in%20Seoni%20district%2C%20who%20is%20vocal%20on%20farmer-related%20issues%2C%20also%20does%20not%20know%20that%20any%20department%20is%20working%20to%20spread%20happiness%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20a%20long%20discussion%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20recall%20the%20announcement%20regarding%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20department%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20remember.%20I%20had%20heard%20many%20years%20ago%20that%20a%20Ministry%20of%20Happiness%20would%20be%20set%20up.%20Has%20it%20already%20been%20made%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20he%20was%20told%20in%20detail%20about%20the%20programs%20of%20the%20department%2C%20he%20said%20that%20no%20such%20program%20has%20been%20organised%20in%20his%20area.%20%E2%80%9CLeave%20aside%20%E2%80%98Anand%20Sabha%E2%80%99%20in%20schools%2C%20our%20village%20school%20itself%20has%20been%20closed.%20Children%20are%20upset%20and%20stressed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20farmer%20faces%20different%20types%20of%20challenges%20throughout%20the%20year.%20He%20is%20in%20dire%20need%20of%20some%20such%20initiative%20which%20can%20relieve%20him%20of%20stress%20and%20make%20him%20happy%2C%20but%20leave%20aside%20the%20common%20farmer%20even%20a%20socially%20and%20politically%20active%20farmer%20like%20me%20does%20not%20know%20of%20any%20such%20department%20nor%20has%20any%20information%20about%20its%20programs%20and%20events.%20No%20villager%20will%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20about%20the%20activities%20of%20this%20department%2C%20when%20and%20where%20its%20programs%20are%20held.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20the%20department%20claims%20to%20organise%20an%20%E2%80%98Anand%20Utsav%E2%80%99%20in%2010%2C000%20gram%20panchayats%2C%20and%20also%20runs%20a%20program%20called%20%E2%80%98Anand%20Gram%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERakesh%20Malviya%20of%20Vikas%20Samvad%2C%20a%20Bhopal-based%20NGO%20working%20on%20nutrition%2C%20health%2C%20women%20and%20child%20rights%20and%20civil%20rights%20in%20MP%2C%20knew%20about%20the%20department%20but%20has%20not%20seen%20any%20activity%20or%20event%20organised%20by%20it.%20When%20asked%20about%20the%20department%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHad%20the%20department%20actually%20existed%2C%20there%20was%20some%20use%20in%20discussing%20it.%20But%20it%20only%20exists%20on%20paper%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20it%2C%20and%20till%20date%20its%20implementation%20has%20not%20been%20seen%20on%20the%20ground.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20whether%20it%20even%20exists%20or%20not.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERTI%20activist%20Ajay%20Dubey%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20common%20man%20is%20not%20aware%20of%20it%20because%20neither%20has%20happiness%20increased%20in%20his%20life%20nor%20does%20he%20believe%20it.%20This%20department%20has%20no%20place%20in%20his%20dictionary.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20senior%20correspondent%20of%20a%20prominent%20media%20house%20of%20the%20state%20based%20in%20Bhopal%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20first%20year%20it%20seemed%20that%20something%20was%20being%20done.%20An%20MoU%20was%20signed%20with%20IIT%20(Kharagpur)%20for%20working%20on%20the%20happiness%20index.%20Workshops%20were%20organised%20by%20inviting%20people%20from%20Bhutan%2C%20America%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%20But%20after%20that%20everything%20stopped.%20No%20one%20knows%20what%20the%20people%20of%20the%20department%20are%20doing%2C%20or%20when%20an%20event%20is%20being%20organised%20and%20where.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20most%20interesting%20thing%20is%20that%20fellow%20party%20members%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20who%20not%20only%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20department%20but%20also%20heads%20it%2C%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20its%20functioning.%20When%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20asked%20the%20BJP%20state%20spokesperson%20Rajpal%20Sisodia%20regarding%20the%20department%20and%20the%20happiness%20index%20not%20being%20released%20yet%2C%20he%20asked%20whether%20we%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20department%20officials.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20he%20was%20told%20that%20the%20officials%20did%20not%20have%20any%20clear%20answer%2C%20he%20listed%20the%20various%20schemes%20run%20by%20the%20state%20and%20central%20governments%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20our%20government%20has%20done%20welfare%20work%20for%20the%20poor%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20has%20brought%20about%20joy%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20people.%20For%20example%2C%20someone%20gets%20a%20building%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana%20or%20Rs.%201%2C250%20are%20deposited%20in%20some%20woman%E2%80%99s%20account%20under%20the%20Ladli%20Behna%20Yojana%20or%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20development%20of%20extremely%20backward%20tribal%20communities%20like%20Baiga%2C%20Sahariya%2C%20Bhariya%2C%20then%20it%20is%20all%20about%20happiness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20he%20failed%20to%20give%20an%20answer%20as%20to%20what%20work%20the%20Department%20of%20Happiness%20was%20doing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20associated%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20parent%20organisation%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20whose%20volunteers%20are%20known%20to%20work%20actively%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20also%20denied%20witnessing%20any%20activity%20of%20the%20department.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEndless%20wait%20for%20happiness%20index%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20department%2C%20it%20was%20claimed%20that%20releasing%20the%20happiness%20index%20would%20be%20its%20priority.%20Apart%20from%20signing%20the%20MoU%20with%20IIT%20Kharagpur%2C%20the%20then%20officials%20had%20also%20visited%20Bhutan%20at%20government%20expense.%20But%20so%20far%20there%20has%20been%20no%20outcome.%20Citing%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20and%20other%20reasons%20for%20delay%2C%20the%20Anand%20Sansthan%20repeatedly%20assured%20that%20the%20index%20would%20be%20released%20soon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChief%20Executive%20Officer%20(CEO)%20of%20the%20institute%2C%20Akhilesh%20Argal%20gave%20the%20same%20assurance%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20said%20that%20all%20preparations%20are%20complete%2C%20and%20the%20index%20will%20be%20released%20after%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20department%E2%80%99s%20seriousness%20regarding%20the%20index%20can%20be%20understood%20from%20it%20annual%20report%20published%20on%20their%20website%20on%20August%2021%2C%202023.%20It%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20institute%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20IIT%20Kharagpur%2C%20has%20prepared%20the%20necessary%20questionnaire%20for%20the%20happiness%20index%20and%20the%20survey%20work%20will%20be%20undertaken%20once%20the%20situation%20becomes%20normal%20after%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20means%20that%20the%20department%20believes%20that%20the%20situation%20of%20Covid-19%20infections%20still%20persists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20intent%20can%20also%20be%20gauged%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20of%20the%2028%20posts%20sanctioned%20for%20the%20department%2C%2013%20are%20vacant.%20More%20importantly%2C%20%2C%20among%20the%2017%20postings%20mentioned%20on%20the%20website%2C%20seven%20are%20vacant.%20Of%20these%207%20positions%2C%202%20out%20of%203%20posts%20related%20to%20the%20happiness%20index%20are%20vacant.%20Even%20the%20post%20of%20Director%20of%20happiness%20index%20is%20vacant.%20Though%20there%20was%20great%20emphasis%20on%20research%20in%20the%20concept%20of%20spreading%20happiness%2C%20the%20post%20of%20research%20director%20is%20vacant%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20institute%20also%20issues%20the%20%E2%80%98Anand%20Research%20Fellowship%E2%80%99%20to%20promote%20research%20on%20happiness%2C%20but%20no%20research%20papers%20have%20been%20published%20till%20date.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20budget%20to%20bring%20happiness%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%20is%2010%20paisa%20per%20person%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20happiness%20department%20was%20first%20established%20as%20an%20independent%20department%20but%20after%20the%20government%20changed%20in%202018%2C%20it%20was%20merged%20into%20the%20spirituality%20department.%20When%20the%20BJP%20returned%20to%20power%20in%202020%2C%20the%20department%20was%20made%20independent%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022-23%2C%20a%20budget%20of%20Rs%205%20crore%20was%20allotted%20to%20it%2C%20of%20which%20Rs%202%20crore%20was%20for%20salary%20payment%2C%20office%20rent%2C%20electricity%20and%20water%20costs%2C%20publication%20and%20advertising.%20There%20was%20a%20nutrition%20grant%20worth%20Rs%203%20crore%2C%20with%20which%20the%20department%20was%20supposed%20to%20conduct%20programs%20to%20spread%20happiness.%20However%2C%20the%20department%20spent%20only%20Rs%204.22%20crore%20of%20the%20total%20budget.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20that%20the%20available%20documents%20of%20the%20financial%20year%202021-22%20show%20that%20only%20Rs%2079%20lakh%20was%20spent%20on%20all%20the%20programs%20run%20by%20this%20ambitious%20department%20of%20the%20CM%20to%20spread%20happiness.%20This%20translates%20to%20roughly%200.10%20paisa%20per%20person%20when%20estimated%20for%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%20of%20about%208%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Argal%20considers%20this%20budget%20adequate.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20through%20volunteers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CA%20new%20concept%20is%20being%20introduced%2C%20it%20will%20definitely%20take%20time.%20The%20budget%20is%20sufficient%20for%20us%2C%20there%20is%20no%20problem.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Anand%20Department%E2%80%99%20for%20whom%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20government%20servants%20have%20registered%20as%20volunteer%20anandaks%2C%20which%20is%20more%20than%2040%25%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20Dainik%20Bhaskar.%20Among%20them%2C%20the%20number%20of%20education%20department%20personnel%20is%20even%20more.%20Non-government%20persons%20include%20grassroots%20activists%2C%20like%20social%20workers%20and%20journalists.%20In%20the%20list%20of%20268%20anandam%20associates%20available%20on%20the%20website%2C%20more%20than%2060%25%20are%20government%20employees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20the%20program%20leaders%20guiding%20anandam%20associates%20are%20government%20servants.%20Out%20of%20the%2052%20district%20contact%20persons%2C%2048%20are%20also%20government%20servants.%20According%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDainik%20Bhaskar%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20only%2010%25%20of%20the%20total%20anandaks%20are%20active%20on%20ground.%20When%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20tried%20to%20contact%20the%20members%20mentioned%20in%20the%20list%20of%20Anand%20associates%2C%20some%20of%20the%20numbers%20were%20unreachable%20while%20others%20said%20that%20they%20were%20no%20longer%20associated%20with%20the%20department.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArgal%20may%20dream%20of%20making%20the%20entire%20scheme%20a%20success%20on%20a%20volunteer%20basis%2C%20but%20the%20%E2%80%98non-official%20anandam%20associate%E2%80%99%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20take%20out%20time%20from%20our%20work%20and%20try%20to%20spread%20happiness%20among%20people%20for%20our%20mental%20satisfaction%2C%20then%20the%20department%20should%20at%20least%20pay%20for%20our%20food%20and%20conveyance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBarkha%20Dangi%2C%20an%20anandam%20associate%20from%20the%20Bhopal%20division%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20offered%20training%20by%20the%20Anand%20Sansthan%20which%20used%20to%20be%20free%20earlier%20but%20now%20we%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20it.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20there%20is%20the%20cost%20of%20traveling%20to%20and%20from%20Bhopal%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20cost%20of%20stay%20for%20the%20four-day%20training%20session.%20With%20all%20this%20expenditure%2C%20people%E2%80%99s%20interest%20in%20volunteering%20has%20started%20waning.%20Other%20people%20had%20got%20associated%20because%20of%20us%2C%20but%20now%20they%20have%20distanced%20themselves.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Argal%20refutes%20these%20allegations%20as%20baseless%20and%20denies%20taking%20any%20kind%20of%20fee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20another%20Anand%20associate%20Vikas%20Yadav%2C%20who%20is%20a%20social%20worker%20from%20Katni%2C%20also%20made%20a%20similar%20remark.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20initiative%20was%20good%20but%20the%20government%20servants%20associated%20with%20it%20(anandaks)%20do%20not%20understand%20its%20importance.%20They%20think%20that%20it%20is%20just%20training.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAjay%20Dubey%20alleges%20that%20relatives%20of%20government%20officials%20are%20working%20in%20the%20department.%20He%20claims%20that%20the%20department%20should%20actually%20be%20called%20%E2%80%98Sarkari%20Tantra%20Anand%20Vibhag%E2%80%99%20(Anand%20Department%20for%20Government%20Servants)%20for%20which%20only%20government%20employees%20are%20eligible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20department%20was%20formed%20in%202016-17%2C%20it%20was%20quite%20a%20good%20step.%20Chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20himself%20focused%20on%20it.%20There%20was%20enthusiasm%20about%20it%20among%20the%20common%20people%20as%20well.%20Along%20with%20government%20employees%2C%20common%20people%20were%20also%20given%20equal%20importance%20and%20were%20made%20nodal%20officers%2C%20district%20coordinators%20or%20anandam%20associates.%20Later%2C%20people%20with%20political%20connections%20entered%20the%20scene%20and%20made%20it%20their%20personal%20hub%2C%E2%80%9DDr.%20Sharma%20alleged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EState%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Ravi%20Saxena%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Anand%20Department%20was%20created%20to%20make%20the%20people%20of%20RSS%2C%20a%20subsidiary%20organisation%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20happy.%20Even%20today%20they%20are%20the%20ones%20enjoying%20it.%20No%20one%20from%20the%20state%20got%20any%20benefit.%20It%20does%20nothing%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20public.%20From%20its%20president%20to%20the%20people%20sitting%20in%20the%20executive%2C%20all%20of%20them%20have%20connections%20to%20the%20Sangh%20and%20are%20taking%20advantage%20of%20government%20facilities.%20I%20would%20say%20that%20this%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20organisation%20of%20the%20RSS%20which%20is%20working%20to%20propagate%20its%20ideology.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EStatistics%20also%20tell%20the%20story%20of%20failure%20of%20%E2%80%98Anand%20Department%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NCRB%20data%2C%20suicide%20incidents%20are%20rising%20in%20the%20state%20each%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20department%2C%20the%20suicide%20rate%20in%20the%20state%20was%207.7%25%20in%202015%2C%20which%20increased%20to%209.1%25%20in%202021.%20The%20department%20claims%20maximum%20activism%20among%20government%20employees%20and%20students%2C%20but%20in%202021%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20stood%20second%20in%20the%20country%20in%20terms%20of%20student%20suicides%20and%20fourth%20in%20terms%20of%20suicides%20among%20government%20employees.%20In%202016%2C%20more%20than%202000%20daily%20wage%20earners%20committed%20suicide%20in%20the%20state%2C%20while%20in%202021%20this%20number%20more%20than%20doubled%20to%204%2C657.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20ranks%2017%20among%2019%20states%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fniti-aayog-health-index-2021-see-ranking-of-states-and-uts-based-on-performance-101640601217921.html%5C%22%3ENITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20Health%20Index%202020-21%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%20index%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20the%20seventh%20worst%20performing%20state%20in%20the%20field%20of%20education%2C%20even%20though%20mostly%20teachers%20and%20students%20are%20associated%20with%20the%20happiness%20department.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20figures%20are%20enough%20to%20show%20how%20much%20happiness%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20Anand%20Department%2C%20functioning%20right%20under%20his%20nose%2C%20has%20been%20able%20to%20peddle%20happiness%20among%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%