20to%20free%20the%20200-odd%20hostages%20taken%20by%20Hamas%20during%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%20Israel's%20military%20spokesperson%20Daniel%20Hagari%20has%20said%20the%20bombardment%20in%20Gaza%20will%20be%20intensified%20to%20minimise%20risks%20to%20troops%20when%20they%20enter%20the%20Strip%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported.%20The%20officer%20called%20upon%20Gaza%20city%20residents%20to%20move%20south%20for%20their%20safety.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EPalestinians%20have%20received%20renewed%20warnings%20from%20Israel's%20forces%20to%20move%20to%20the%20south%20of%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20has%20reported.%20The%20fresh%20warning%20adds%20that%20they%20could%20be%20identified%20as%20sympathisers%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20organisation%26quot%3B%20if%20they%20stayed%20put.%20The%20message%20was%20delivered%20in%20leaflets%20marked%20with%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20name%20and%20logo%20from%20Saturday%20and%20also%20sent%20to%20people%20via%20mobile%20phone%20audio%20messages.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHamas%20on%20Friday%20released%20two%20hostages%20--%20US%20citizens%20Judith%20Tai%20Raanan%20and%20her%20daughter%20Natalie%20Shoshana%20Raanan.%20The%20mother-daughter%20pair%20was%20kidnapped%20from%20Nahal%20Oz%20kibbutz%20near%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20border%20on%20October%207.%20They%20were%20reportedly%20visiting%20Israel%20on%20a%20holiday.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHamas%20has%20now%20claimed%20that%20they%20had%20offered%20to%20release%20two%20more%20hostages%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds%2C%20but%20Israel%20declined.%20A%20Reuters%20report%20has%20quoted%20Abu%20Ubaida%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20Hamas'%20armed%20wing%2C%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20organisation%20had%20informed%20Qatar%20of%20its%20intention%20to%20release%20two%20more%20hostages.%20Qatar%20mediated%20the%20release%20of%20the%20US%20citizens%20Friday.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20Israeli%20government%20has%20termed%20the%20Hamas%20claim%20as%20%26quot%3Bpropaganda%26quot%3B.%20Israel%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20office%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20refer%20to%20false%20propaganda%20by%20Hamas.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20continue%20to%20act%20in%20every%20way%20to%20return%20all%20the%20kidnapped%20and%20missing%20people%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAs%20the%20unrest%20in%20the%20region%20spirals%2C%20Israel's%20bombings%20also%20put%20two%20airports%20in%20Syria%20out%20of%20service%2C%20AFP%20reported%20quoting%20Syrian%20state%20media.%20Government-controlled%20airports%20in%20Damascus%20and%20Aleppo%20are%20out%20of%20service%20and%20Syria's%20transport%20ministry%20has%20said%20flights%20were%20re-routed%20to%20Latakia.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20airstrikes%20in%20Syria%20are%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20warning%20to%20its%20ally%20Iran%2C%20seen%20to%20back%20groups%20such%20as%20Hamas%20and%20Hezbollah.%20Hezbollah%20has%20been%20exchanging%20fire%20with%20Israel%20across%20its%20border%20with%20Lebanon%20and%20has%20warned%20of%20a%20bigger%20role%20in%20the%20war.%20Israel%20has%20said%20Hezbollah%20is%20dragging%20Lebanon%20%26quot%3Binto%20a%20war%20that%20it%20will%20gain%20nothing%20from%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIsrael%20today%20bombed%20a%20mosque%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Liberation%20Organisation.%20Tel%20Aviv%20has%20said%20the%20strike%20on%20Al-Ansar%20mosque%20in%20Jenin%20had%20killed%20%26quot%3Bterror%20operatives%26quot%3B%20from%20Hamas%20and%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20AFP%20reported.%20The%20Palestinian%20health%20ministry%20said%20two%20men%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20strike.%20About%2084%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20area%20of%20Palestine%20since%20the%20war%20began.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHamas'%20stronghold%20Gaza%20is%20facing%20unprecedented%20devastation%20as%20Israel%20strikes%20back.%20The%20narrow%20Strip%20that%20houses%20about%202%20million%20people%20was%20un