oc%20was%20at%20the%20central%20level%20and%20its%20focus%20was%20on%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20clearly%20miffed%20SP%20chief%20continued%20to%20attack%20the%20Congress%20on%20Friday%2C%20asking%2C%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Congress%20behaves%20like%20this%2C%20who%20will%20stand%20with%20them%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20the%20Congress%20should%20not%20%26quot%3Bbetray%26quot%3B%20the%20Samajwadi%20party%20and%20asked%20it%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20whether%20it%20wanted%20an%20alliance%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20received%20a%20message%20from%20someone%20through%20the%20senior-most%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%20If%20he%20is%20saying%20something%2C%20I%20will%20have%20to%20follow.%20He%20gave%20some%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%2C%20without%20revealing%20any%20name%20or%20explaining%20further.%20%26quot%3BBut%20one%20thing%20I%20want%20to%20say%20is%3A%20why%20did%20they%20call%20us%20if%20they%20did%20not%20want%20an%20alliance%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20not%20conspire%20against%20us%2C%20don't%20betray%20us.%20They%20should%20tell%20us%20straight%20that%20they%20don't%20need%20Samajwadis.%20I%20promise%20you%20that%20we%20will%20not%20talk%20about%20alliance%20even%20once%20and%20will%20begin%20preparation%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20on%20our%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20also%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20Congress%20over%20its%20support%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20and%20said%20it%20was%20a%20miracle%20that%20the%20party%20wanted%20it%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20same%20Congress%20party%20that%20did%20not%20give%20the%20numbers%20of%20the%20caste%20census%20earlier.%20Now%20everyone%20knows%20that%20until%20and%20unless%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20support%20of%20the%20backward%20castes%20and%20tribes%2C%20you%20won't%20succeed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said