0a%20network%20of%20armed%20proxy%20groups%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20from%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%20to%20the%20Houthis%20in%20Yemen%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIranian%20inaction%20on%20the%20ground%20could%20be%20perceived%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20weakness%20by%20those%20proxy%20forces%2C%20which%20have%20been%20Tehran's%20principal%20weapon%20of%20influence%20in%20the%20region%20for%20decades%2C%20according%20to%20three%20officials.%20They%20said%20it%20could%20also%20dent%20the%20standing%20of%20Iran%2C%20which%20has%20long%20championed%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20against%20Israel%2C%20a%20country%20it%20refuses%20to%20recognise%20and%20casts%20as%20an%20evil%20occupier.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Iranians%20are%20facing%20this%20dilemma%20of%20whether%20they%20are%20going%20to%20send%20Hezbollah%20to%20the%20fight%20in%20order%20to%20try%20to%20save%20their%20arm%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20or%20maybe%20they%20are%20going%20to%20let%20go%20of%20this%20arm%20and%20give%20it%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Avi%20Melamed%2C%20a%20former%20Israeli%20intelligence%20official%20and%20a%20negotiator%20during%20the%20first%20and%20second%20intifadas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20point%20where%20the%20Iranians%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BCalculating%20their%20risks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Survival%20Is%20Utmost%20Priority'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIran's%20strategic%20goals%20are%20countered%20by%20immediate%20military%20considerations%20as%20Israel%20-%20responding%20to%20Hamas'%20devastating%20attack%20on%20Oct.%207%20that%20killed%201%2C400%20Israelis%20-%20has%20unleashed%20an%20aerial%20blitz%20on%20Gaza%2C%20killing%20at%20least%204%2C300%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20-%20a%20major%20military%20power%20-%20is%20widely%20believed%20to%20have%20its%20own%20nuclear%20arsenal%2C%20though%20it%20will%20neither%20confirm%20nor%20deny%20this%2C%20and%20has%20the%20support%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20has%20moved%20two%20aircraft%20carriers%20and%20fighter%20jets%20to%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%2C%20partly%20as%20a%20warning%20to%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Iran's%20top%20leaders%2C%20especially%20the%20supreme%20leader%20(Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei)%2C%20the%20utmost%20priority%20is%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20Iranian%20diplomat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20Iranian%20authorities%20have%20used%20strong%20rhetoric%20against%20Israel%20since%20the%20attack%20started%2C%20but%20they%20have%20refrained%20from%20direct%20military%20involvement%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20Oct.%207%2C%20Hezbollah%20has%20exchanged%20fire%20with%20Israeli%20forces%20along%20the%20Lebanese-Israeli%20frontier%20in%20clashes%20that%20have%20killed%2014%20of%20the%20Islamist%20group's%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20sources%20familiar%20with%20Hezbollah's%20thinking%20said%20the%20low-level%20violence%20was%20designed%20to%20keep%20Israeli%20forces%20busy%20but%20not%20open%20a%20major%20new%20front%2C%20with%20one%20characterising%20the%20tactic%20as%20waging%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20wars%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20leader%20Sayyed%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for%20issuing%20threats%20against%20Israel%20in%20speeches%2C%20has%20not%20given%20a%20public%20address%20since%20the%20crisis%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%20senior%20Israeli%20security%20sources%20and%20a%20Western%20security%20source%20told%20Reuters%20that%20Israel%20didn't%20want%20a%20direct%20confrontation%20with%20Tehran%20and%20that%20while%20the%20Iranians%20had%20trained%20and%20armed%20Hamas%2C%20there%20was%20no%20indication%20that%20they%20had%20prior%20knowledge%20of%20the%20Oct.%207%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhamenei%2C%20the%20supreme%20leader%2C%20has%20denied%20Iran%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20attack%2