eful%20resolution%20to%20the%20Palestine%20issue.%20Multiple%20experts%20have%20said%20the%20normalisation%20of%20Israel-Saudi%20Arabia%20relations%2C%20which%20was%20paused%20due%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20was%20a%20crucial%20backdrop%20against%20which%20Hamas%20planned%20its%20unprecedented%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Saudi%20prince%20minced%20no%20words%20in%20his%20criticism%20of%20Israel%20for%20its%20counterstrike%20that%20targeted%20innocent%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20West%20Bank.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20wrongs%20don't%20make%20a%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECountering%20the%20US%20media's%20use%20of%20%26quot%3Bunprovoked%20attack%26quot%3B%20to%20describe%20Hamas'%20offensive%20in%20Israel%2C%20Faisal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20more%20provocation%20is%20required%20to%20make%20it%20provoked%20than%20what%20Israel%20has%20done%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20for%20three-quarters%20of%20a%20century%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFlagging%20Israel's%20alleged%20excesses%20in%20Palestine%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20civilians%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20bloodletting%20must%20stop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20condemn%20Israel's%20stealing%20of%20Palestinian%20lands%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20further%20accusing%20Tel%20Aviv%20of%20targeted%20killings%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20jailing%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Saudi%20prince%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20Western%20politicians%20for%20%26quot%3Bshedding%20tears%26quot%3B%20when%20Israelis%20are%20killed%20by%20Palestinians%20but%20%26quot%3Brefusing%20to%20even%20express%20sorrow%26quot%3B%20when%20it's%20the%20other%20way%20around.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20heroes%20in%20this%20conflict%2C%20only%20victims%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFaisal%20led%20the%20Saudi%20intelligence%20agency%20Al%20Mukhabarat%20Al%20'Ammah%20for%2024%20years%20and%20also%20served%20as%20the%20country's%20ambassador%20to%20London%20and%20t