anonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332610%2Frajasthan-software-engineer-earns-crores-by-making-traditional-kulhad-business-chai-tea%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Indians%20Innovating%20With%20Millets%20to%20Make%20Them%20Appealing%20%26amp%3B%20Help%20Farmers%20Earn%20Big%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMillets%20are%20a%20superfood%20that%20are%20rich%20in%20protein%20and%20offer%20a%20plethora%20of%20benefits%20to%20the%20farmers%20who%20grow%20them%2C%20and%20to%20the%20people%20who%20consume%20them.%20India%20is%20the%20top%20producer%20of%20these%20sustainable%20grains%20that%20are%20a%20good%20source%20of%20essential%20nutrients.%20This%20year%20is%20the%20International%20Year%20of%20Millets%2C%20and%20the%20Food%20and%20Agriculture%20Organisation%20(FAO)%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20is%20creating%20awareness%20about%20millets%20as%20affordable%20foods%20that%20contribute%20to%20a%20healthy%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20differentiates%20millets%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20thrive%20in%20harsh%20growing%20conditions%20and%20are%20climate%20resilient.%20They%20require%20much%20less%20water%20than%20grains%20like%20rice%20and%20wheat.%20The%20FAO%20says%20that%20millets%20provide%20antioxidants%2C%20minerals%2C%20fibre%2C%20iron%20and%20protein%2C%20alongside%20being%20gluten-free%20with%20a%20low-glycaemic%20index.%20They%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325105%2Fhyderabad-entrepreneur-raju-bhupati-makes-affordable-troo-good-millet-snacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomical%20for%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20require%20less%20water%20and%20fewer%20pesticides%2C%20becoming%20a%20boon%20to%20small%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMillets%20are%20India%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20food%20grain%2C%20grown%20across%20the%20country.%20They%20were%20sidelined%20over%20the%20years%2C%20but%20now%20the%20focus%20is%20squarely%20back%20on%20how%20one%20can%20use%20these%20grains%20in%20their%20diet%20and%20farmers%20are%20switching%20back%20to%20growing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20change%20are%20Indians%20who%20are%20bringing%20millets%20back%20to%20the%20spotlight%20through%20their%20innovations.%20They%20are%20delivering%20millets%20in%20new%2C%20interesting%20ways%2C%20helping%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20five%20Indians%20championing%20the%20humble%20grain%20through%20their%20startups%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVeer%20Shetty%20Biradar%2C%20SS%20Bhavani%20Foods%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20583px)%20100vw%2C%20583px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22583%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Veer%20Shetty%20Biradar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186.jpeg%20583w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186-178x300.jpeg%20178w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186-500x843.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186-150x253.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-277461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22983%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVeer%20Shetty%20Biradar%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Millet%20Man.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20family%20of%20farmers